Quick History Lesson on Shallow/Deep Copies


# Create a copy (memory inefficient)
pums_nocopy &lt;- pums

# Modify by reference (memory efficient)
pums[, age_decade := floor(AGEP / 10) * 10]

# shows up in pums_nocopy
pums_nocopy[, .(age_decade)]

